  "idle.annoyingvillagers.flapping_emote.9": "我曾师从一群迷茫的鸡咪。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.flapping_emote.10": "如果热情能飞翔，我早已远去。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.flapping_emote.11": "挥动是一种心态。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.flapping_emote.12": "空气动力学可有可无。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.flapping_emote.13": "我比物理学更相信自己。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.flapping_emote.14": "这要么是艺术，要么是危机。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.flapping_emote.15": "我只差一次拍打就能成为伟大。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.flapping_emote.16": "别笑，这是严肃的鸟类事务。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.flapping_emote.17": "天空拒绝了我，但我不放弃。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.flapping_emote.18": "见证命运的翩然飞舞。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.flapping_emote.19": "我扇动，所以我存在。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.flapping_emote.20": "也许我一直这样做，重力会道歉。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.fun_jump_emote.1": "哇哦！跳得真棒！",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.fun_jump_emote.2": "有时候你就是得闪人。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.fun_jump_emote.3": "先跳再说！",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.fun_jump_emote.4": "那个小跳跃瞬间改善了我的心情。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.fun_jump_emote.5": "快乐藏在膝盖里。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.fun_jump_emote.6": "看我！我飞起来了！",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.fun_jump_emote.7": "这就是我庆祝活着的方式。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.fun_jump_emote.8": "再跳一步，迈向伟大。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.fun_jump_emote.9": "你能听出着陆时的喜悦。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.fun_jump_emote.10": "每天一次欢乐跳跃，驱散所有阴霾。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.fun_jump_emote.11": "我对那次弹跳毫无遗憾。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.fun_jump_emote.12": "只是为这一天增添一些额外的兴奋感。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.fun_jump_emote.13": "竖起的热情！",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.fun_jump_emote.14": "那跳跃真有个性。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.fun_jump_emote.15": "心情：蓄势待发。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.fun_jump_emote.16": "我基本上就是一只快乐的史莱姆。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.fun_jump_emote.17": "小巧发射，氛围满满。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.fun_jump_emote.18": "这就是休闲物理。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.fun_jump_emote.19": "跳起来，因为站着太无聊了。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.fun_jump_emote.20": "这次跳跃满载情感创伤的恢复力量。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.jump_emote.1": "我要飞起来啦！",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.jump_emote.2": "干净利落的跳跃。简单而有效。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.jump_emote.3": "有时候，高度就是答案。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.jump_emote.4": "快速跳跃，清晰思路。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.jump_emote.5": "永远不要低估一次稳健的跳跃。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.jump_emote.6": "那简直是教科书式操作。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.jump_emote.7": "适当的跳跃让血液流动起来。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.jump_emote.8": "脚步轻盈。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.jump_emote.9": "稍微提一提没什么坏处。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.jump_emote.10": "利落一跃，稳稳落地。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.jump_emote.11": "势不可挡。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.jump_emote.12": "小跃一跳，更佳视野。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.jump_emote.13": "只是确认一下重力还在作用。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.jump_emote.14": "姿势不错，跳得好。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.jump_emote.15": "每一次跳跃，都始于坚定的决心。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.jump_emote.16": "直直向上，再直落下来。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.jump_emote.17": "换口气，清清脑子。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.jump_emote.18": "精准跳跃，动作干净利落。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.jump_emote.19": "这才是正确的操作。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.jump_emote.20": "轻快步伐，迅捷跳跃。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.prone_emote.1": "保持低姿态，保持生存。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.prone_emote.2": "俯卧姿势。战术性与戏剧感兼备。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.prone_emote.3": "紧贴地面的目标难以命中。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.prone_emote.4": "这就是战场智慧的巅峰。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.prone_emote.5": "低调行事，高存活率。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.prone_emote.6": "我不是在躲藏，我是在布阵。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.prone_emote.7": "泥土现在是我的盟友。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.prone_emote.8": "战术煎饼模式已启动。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.prone_emote.9": "看不清的，怎会怀念。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.prone_emote.10": "隐藏身形是一门艺术。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.prone_emote.11": "我更喜欢将危险留在地面。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.prone_emote.12": "平稳、安静且极具目的性。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.prone_emote.13": "地面提供极佳的掩护。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.prone_emote.14": "这个动作表达了我对生存的认真态度。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.prone_emote.15": "有时候，最聪明的选择是向下。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.prone_emote.16": "混乱来临，我已做好准备。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.prone_emote.17": "潜行始于降低身形。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.prone_emote.18": "有人称之为倒地，有人称之为天才。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.prone_emote.19": "这不是恐惧。这是策略。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.prone_emote.20": "我擅长横向战术。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.salute_emote.1": "敬礼！",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.salute_emote.2": "敬人者，人恒敬之。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.salute_emote.3": "为了荣誉与责任。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.salute_emote.4": "严肃时刻的利落敬礼。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.salute_emote.5": "挺立致敬。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.salute_emote.6": "纪律存在于细节中。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.salute_emote.7": "这是一种充满意义的敬礼。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.salute_emote.8": "尊敬，恰到好处地传达。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.salute_emote.9": "永远不要忘记你的原则。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.salute_emote.10": "荣耀至上。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.salute_emote.11": "坚定的敬礼传达了很多信息。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.salute_emote.12": "锐利之形，聚焦更锋利。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.salute_emote.13": "有些时刻值得敬重。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.salute_emote.14": "这敬礼献给勇者。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.salute_emote.15": "庄重、自豪且精准。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.salute_emote.16": "职责已确认。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.salute_emote.17": "规范敬礼，百发百中。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.salute_emote.18": "坚守阵地，敬礼不变。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.salute_emote.19": "尊重是必须的。",
  "idle.annoyingvillagers.salute_emote.20": "背脊挺直，手稳如磐，目标明确。"
}